{"tid":2156444,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【餵狗】亞洲國際餐飲集團 你今日食咗未啊","createTime":"2020-08-14T12:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-14T15:01:10.000Z","uid":84408,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"25642b7c53085af23c439839d9b9028ff161bc61","tid":2156444,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:24:16.000Z","msg":"亞洲國際餐飲集團強制員工做dna檢測，唔驗就唔俾返工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2156339/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2156339/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n早響一年前 <br />\n呢一個集團一做已經有前科打壓遊行同埋運動<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n發夢夢見有連鎖餐飲集團禁員工遊行：<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1325706/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1325706/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n集團現擁有不同的餐廳品牌, 包括:<br />\n- 港式速食餐廳之『百份百餐廳』、<br />\n- 新派歐日融合式的『意樂餐廳』、<br />\n- 重新包裝、與時俱進之『桃園』、及<br />\n- 現場直接烘焙、新鮮現造之『Smile Bread &ndash;百份百烘焙大師』<br />\n<br />\n咁高質嘅餐廳緊係支持啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5a85f45c6e40e635b33884d56d70283f094518e","tid":2156444,"uid":84408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:31:09.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8845ec04cb616e4e3433649ac9b019b93b65b08b","tid":2156444,"uid":118553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:31:45.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1cc39cfc4fddbd5cd5b3924d578a445029338923","tid":2156444,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T12:33:57.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00de64ec274c5958856a3bf6c43fc6ca95a464ae","tid":2156444,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c